    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>Nov. 20. 1867</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">My dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Your favor came<lb/> duly to hand. I was aware<lb/> of my
                subscription to the publication<lb/> of your Books and not having<lb/> received a
                complete set notified you<lb/> of the missing volumes. I do<lb/> not desire the
                number of volumes<lb/> which you propose sending me, &amp;<lb/> if it is the same to
                you, would<lb/> like 1 set complete of Discourses say 10 Vols<lb/> 2 Jews &amp;
                mosaic laws. 3 Instructions.<lb/> 3 Daily Prayer Books &amp; one Bible<lb/> for my
                subscription of one hundred</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>dollars which is herewith enclosed<lb/> with Five 25/100 Dolls for Bible for<lb/>
                <persName>Frances</persName><add>?</add>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I regret that your<lb/> health is not improved, but hope<lb/> that
                your life may be spared<lb/> for many years &amp; that you<lb/> may realize all your
                hopes in<lb/> your new undertakings.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I beg of you not to entertain<lb/> the substitution of the
                Prayer<lb/> Books for the discourses if not<lb/> to your interest.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mr. Nacham</persName> &amp; family join<lb/> with me in
                best wishes for<lb/> your welfare &amp; speedy restoration</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>to health.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I am my dear sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Benj Nathan</persName>
            </p>
            <p>Check No. 83 on 2nd National Bk<lb/> to you order for 105.25</p>
            <pb n="Envelope"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Penn.</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
